{"lemma":"طَرْفَةً","slug":"طَرْفَةً","root":"ط.ر.ف","root_slug":"ط-ر-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-ر-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26608","n26618","n26619","n26620"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8B"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"tamarisk (Tamarix spp.)","tags":["collective"],"examples":[{"text":"وأما غراسة الأرز وهو الذي يسمى السرول\nقال هو نوعان أحدهما يشبه الطرفاء والآخر يشبه العرعر","english":"About the planting of the cedar which is called cypress\nthere are two kinds, one resembles the tamarisk and the other resembles the juniper."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of طَرِيف (ṭarīf)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"masculine plural of طَرِيف (ṭarīf)","tags":["form-of","masculine","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From أَطْرَاف (ʔaṭrāf, “tips, extremes, limbs”), because of its dainty, lengthy extremities, jutting out from the terrains’ ledges."},"ipa":["/tˤar.faːʔ/","/tˤu.ra.faːʔ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26608","headword_ar":"طرّفهُ","root":"Trf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[from the subst."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~arofu","text_ar":"الطَّرْفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning “ the eye ”]: see 1, latter half.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tr~f","text_ar":"طرّف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~arafu","text_ar":"الطَّرَفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, O, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taToriyfN","text_ar":"تَطْرِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, S, O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fought around the army;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because he charges upon, or assaults, those who form the side, or flank, or extreme portion, of it, (S, O, K,) and drives them back upon the main body: (S, O:) or, as in the M,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he fought the most remote thereof, and those that formed the side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flank, thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tr~f EalaY~a AlA_ibila","text_ar":"طرّف عَلَىَّ الاـِبِلَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drove,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sent, back to me those that formed the sides,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extreme portions, of the camels."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tr~f Alxayola","text_ar":"طرّف الخَيْلَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drove back the foremost of the horsemen"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon, the hindmost of them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) Accord. to El-Mufaddal,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taToriyfN","text_ar":"تَطْرِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies a man's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repelling"},{"kind":"text","text":"another man from the hindmost of his companions: (O, TA: *) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tar~ifo Ean~aA h`*aA AlfaArisa","text_ar":"طَرِّفْ عَنَّا هٰذَا الفَارِسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Repel thou from our rear this horseman"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, TA.) ―         -b3-  For another signification [from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~arafu","text_ar":"الطَّرَفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] see 4. ―         -b4-  [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tr~ft banaAnahaA","text_ar":"طرّفت بَنَانَهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a woman)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tinged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dyed, the ends"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aToraAf","text_ar":"اَطْرَاف"},{"kind":"text","text":", O, Msb, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of her fingers with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hin~aA='","text_ar":"حِنَّا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, Msb, K, * TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taToriyfo","text_ar":"تَطْرِيفْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^u*uni","text_ar":"الاُذُنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The making the ear"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a horse"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be pointed, tapering,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slender at the extremity."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [Hence,] Khálid Ibn-Safwán said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayoru AlkalaAmi","text_ar":"خَيْرُ الكَلَامِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Tur~ifato maEaAniyhi wa$ur~ifato mabaAniyhi","text_ar":"مَا طُرِّفَتْ مَعَانِيهِ وَشُرِّفَتْ مَبَانِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The best of language is that of which the meanings are pointed, and of which the constructions are crowned with embellishments as though they were adorned with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uraf","text_ar":"شُرَف"},{"kind":"text","text":", pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$urofapN","text_ar":"شُرْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]. (TA: there mentioned immediately after what here next precedes it.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tr~f Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"طرّف الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TarafN","text_ar":"طَرَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ anything chosen or choice ”] means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He chose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made choice of, the thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tTr~fhu","text_ar":"تطرّفهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA. [See also 10.]) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tr~f","text_ar":"طرّف"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a camel means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He lost his tooth"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"teeth"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (O, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of extreme age."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n26618","headword_ar":"طَرْفَةٌ","root":"Trf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A wink,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a closing of one of the eyelids upon the other:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a twinkling of the eye,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a putting the eyelids in motion"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state of commotion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) One says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoraEu","text_ar":"اَسْرَعُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino Tarofapi EayonK","text_ar":"مِنْ طَرْفَةِ عَيْنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Quicker than a wink,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a twinkling of an eye"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yufaAriquniY Tarofapa","text_ar":"مَا يُفَارِقُنِى طَرْفَةَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayonK","text_ar":"عَيْنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He does not separate himself from me during a wink,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a twinkling of an eye"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A red spot of blood, in the eye, occasioned by a blow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"some other cause."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A brand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mark made with a hot iron, having to it no"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aToraAf","text_ar":"اَطْرَاف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sides,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lateral portions"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being only a line."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, O, K.)       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~arofapu","text_ar":"الطَّرْفَةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain star"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asterism"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najomN","text_ar":"نَجْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"). (K. [There thus mentioned as though different from the asterism commonly called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~arofu","text_ar":"الطَّرْفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which I do not believe to be the case: see the latter appellation.])"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n26619","headword_ar":"طُرْفَةٌ","root":"Trf","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hurt of the eye, occasioning its shedding tears."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Newly-acquired property;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything that one has newly acquired, and that pleases him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uToruwfapN","text_ar":"اُطْرُوفَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing newly acquired;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 54;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that is strange and deemed good;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Id. p. 615;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pleasing rarity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a welcome,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasing, thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gift not given to any one before;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gift of which the recipient did not possess the like, and which pleases him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) [generally,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a novel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rare, and pleasing, present;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"turofapN","text_ar":"تُرْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuHofapN","text_ar":"تُحْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TurafN","text_ar":"طُرَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Har p. 32.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TariyfN","text_ar":"طَرِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TariyfapN","text_ar":"طَرِيفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n26620","headword_ar":"طَرَفَةٌ","root":"Trf","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single tree of the species called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TarofaA='","text_ar":"طَرْفَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. (AHn, S, O, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}